 sub-nanometric clusters Mg$_n$H$_{2n}$ with $n\n\\leq 10$, with a non-negligible, although little effect due to anharmonicities\n(up to 10%).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 27 Nov 2021 18:33:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-30"}
